From 9da575021b56af141818ccc856f44fdcb801b884 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: libiao <1102510224@qq.com>
Date: Wed, 8 Apr 2026 16:37:39 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] threadpool: adjust concurrency using scheduler statistics

- backport adaptive threadpool concurrency control from 8.0
- add sysvars for extra threads and scheduler thresholds
- instrument group commit pending waits for threadpool scheduling
- move vcpu detection helper into mysys
- add MTR coverage for the new threadpool sysvars

Tested:
./build/mysql-test/mysql-test-run.pl --suite=sys_vars \
    thread_pool_enable_extra_threads_basic \
    thread_pool_cpu_usage_threshold_basic \
    thread_pool_nvcsw_freq_threshold_basic \
    thread_pool_nivcsw_freq_threshold_basic

./build/mysql-test/mysql-test-run.pl pool_of_threads
